         <abstract id="aspace_c7f80d077b83651bb6ee2e4965852dee">The History of Theater lecture series was written and delivered by A. M. Nagler, and the series is a condensed version of Professor Nagler's Drama 6 course at the Yale School of Drama.</abstract>
